 {"text": "36.2%", "bbox": [1057.7, 1065.4, 1111.6, 1086.2]}, {"text": "At December 31, 2009, foreign subsidiaries of the Company had net operating loss carryforwards of", "bbox": [185.5, 1123.6, 1022.6, 1144.5]}, {"text": "approximately $42 million. Approximately half of the net operating loss carryforwards expire on various dates", "bbox": [143.8, 1148.6, 1067.6, 1169.5]}, {"text": "through December 31, 2018. The remaining net operating loss carryforwards are not subject to expiration.", "bbox": [143.8, 1173.6, 1029.0, 1194.5]}, {"text": "We believe that it is more likely than not that the benefit from certain foreign net operating loss", "bbox": [185.5, 1219.4, 983.2, 1240.2]}, {"text": "carryforwards will not be realized. In recognition of this risk, we have provided a valuation allowance of $3.3", "bbox": [143.8, 1244.4, 1059.9, 1265.2]}, {"text": "million and $2.2 million at December 31, 2009 and 2008, respectively, on the deferred tax asset relating to these", "bbox": [143.8, 1269.4, 1082.0, 1290.2]}, {"text": "foreign net operating loss carryforwards.", "bbox": [143.8, 1294.4, 484.0, 1315.2]}, {"text": "The Company has undistributed earnings of foreign subsidiaries of approximately $137 million at", "bbox": [185.5, 1340.1, 1002.0, 1361.0]}, {"text": "December 31, 2009 for which deferred taxes have not been provided. These earnings, which are considered to be", "bbox": [143.8, 1365.2, 1087.3, 1386.0]}, {"text": "permanently reinvested, would be subject to U.S. tax if they were remitted as dividends. It is not practicable to", "bbox": [143.8, 1390.2, 1067.1, 1411.0]}, {"text": "determine the deferred tax liability on these earnings.", "bbox": [143.8, 1415.2, 589.3, 1436.0]}, {"text": "67", "bbox": [608.6, 1465.8, 629.4, 1486.6]}]}